text: Jozef Bachleda (born 23 February 1973) is a Slovak skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Slovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Poprad
